## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible factors contributing to income inequality. The data is primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global trends. Additionally, the information is subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may have their own biases or gaps in data. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.